data.title: Winterfest Holiday Lights Tour Map Released
data.text:
The much-anticipated Winterfest Holiday Lights Tour map has been released by The 712 Initiative! You're invited to take a tour of the best holiday lights in Council Bluffs. Enjoy this self-guided event from the safety and warmth of your vehicle at a time that works best for you and your family! Simply click the buttons below to view the route.

PDF/Printable Version

Google Maps Version

For more information about the Holiday Lights Facebook photo contest, click here!

The Winterfest Holiday Lights Tour was created by The 712 Initiative and presented by Centris Federal Credit Union.
